{"tid":345017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【住返老人院】公屋王業主86歲鮑伯伯：「賣樓幫兒子還債」","createTime":"2017-08-02T16:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T18:57:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47b2dee76c86f4d01d65c6d5d08d47358b16f2bf","tid":345017,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170802/large/1501669715_d543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170802%2Flarge%2F1501669715_d543.jpg&h=8aa5c3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將軍澳公屋景林邨景桃樓一個實用面積153方呎，剛以235萬元天價易手，呎價高達1.5萬元，成新界史上最貴公屋王（報道：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vh923p）。原來，業主是一名86歲老伯伯，今次賣樓是幫兒子還債。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vh923p%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D86%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E4%BC%AF%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8A%E6%AC%A1%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E6%98%AF%E5%B9%AB%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E9%82%84%E5%82%B5%E3%80%82&d=q7VntjqcN0D1Vxs6osFulBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=29ae2855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vh923p）。原來，業主是一名86歲老伯伯，今次賣樓是幫兒子還債。</a><br />\n記者於黃昏時分到景林邨景桃樓公屋王單位直擊拍門，見到有一名長者居住，他姓鮑，今年86歲，獨居於此，他承認單位已經賣出，住了此單位4年左右，賣出單位的錢是給予兒子用來還債，十月九日交樓，之後就會搬去元朗老人院生活，月費2000幾元。<br />\n他言帶不滿話「唔知個仔搞咩」，本身住上水老人院，4年前上到樓，買入價十多萬元，自己一個人住呢到，但現時又要住返老人院，不過，他就話無咩唔開心同無咩唔捨得，自己都住過老人院，不擔心適應不到。<br />\n不過，伯伯就表明不知道自己的單位是創新高賣出。伯伯年紀大，行動雖然自如，但他剛剛正在睡覺，只是願意睡在床上接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170802/57032999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170802%2F57032999&d=q7VntjqcN0D1Vxs6osFulBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=8e388ef5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170802%2F57032999&h=d1172a3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170802/57032999</a>"},{"pid":"7e17e47ba40557ba9ca53f977f95b388b3a420bb","tid":345017,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db087c7255d17be02c57b345ae8eb01781b7e40f","tid":345017,"uid":97451,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ce9a743e117aaae6d667f63447bed4ba673ad5d","tid":345017,"uid":61903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"屌 佢個仔死撚左佢好過啦"},{"pid":"4c0e47ec6f15229a03884866dc266be401d0b97d","tid":345017,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:03:27.000Z","msg":"一單新聞竟然有咁多件可悲嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d6a6c44523e1452694dd2c09aad3dbc44a1e71","tid":345017,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64952272ab5f4384772daaa6b13bf05cd9823864","tid":345017,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4年前十幾萬買到?</blockquote><br />\n公屋係呢個價"},{"pid":"774e1aed435eca2ab6a94c2c09db35613860721e","tid":345017,"uid":54904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4年前十幾萬買到?</blockquote><br />\n公屋係呢個價</blockquote><br />\n咁依家要二百幾萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54ba6c187c11868d767ba2c7a101a06b2bdf8ce","tid":345017,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"廢老住多幾年都死架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如賣樓淨番啲錢幫個仔過世<br />\n<br />\n利申：曲，阿伯啲血汗錢俾敗家仔洗晒好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3148d31ebc6945e653e6851be68daa7b0c2084c","tid":345017,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T